# 重構 Route B：徹底刪除舊版導航系統

## Phase 1: MapData DTO 更新
- [ ] 新增 `NavNodeData`, `NavEdgeData` DTO
- [ ] [MapData](file:///d:/Full_end/C%23/ArtaleAI/Models/Map/MapData.cs#9-35) 新增 [Nodes](file:///d:/Full_end/C%23/ArtaleAI/Core/Domain/Navigation/NavigationGraph.cs#120-121), [Edges](file:///d:/Full_end/C%23/ArtaleAI/Core/PathPlanningTracker.cs#274-342) 屬性
- [ ] **保留** `WaypointPaths`, `Connections` 供舊檔相容與編輯器使用

## Phase 2: AppConfig + 遷移工具
- [ ] 新增 `LegacyMapMigrator.cs` 轉換實作與 ActionCode 靜態轉換方法
- [ ] 更新 `AppConfig.LoadMapFromFile()`，若無 Nodes 則呼叫 Migrator 自動升級
- [ ] 更新 `AppConfig.SaveMapToFile()`，使用乾淨的序列化副本避免污染 Editor 狀態

## Phase 3: PathPlanningTracker 重構
- [ ] 更新 [LoadMap()](file:///d:/Full_end/C%23/ArtaleAI/Services/PathPlanningManager.cs#21-30) — 解析 Nodes/Edges 建構 NavigationGraph
- [ ] 刪除 `_pathNodes`, `_currentTarget`, `_currentPathIndex` 等舊欄位
- [ ] 刪除 [SetPlannedPathWithActions()](file:///d:/Full_end/C%23/ArtaleAI/Core/PathPlanningTracker.cs#386-436), [BuildNavigationGraph()](file:///d:/Full_end/C%23/ArtaleAI/Core/PathPlanningTracker.cs#526-693), [ActionCodeToKeys()](file:///d:/Full_end/C%23/ArtaleAI/Core/PathPlanningTracker.cs#559-584)
- [ ] 刪除 [GetNodePriorities()](file:///d:/Full_end/C%23/ArtaleAI/Services/PathPlanningManager.cs#200-208), [FindClosestPathNodeIndex()](file:///d:/Full_end/C%23/ArtaleAI/Core/PathPlanningTracker.cs#1852-1877), [SetPlannedPath()](file:///d:/Full_end/C%23/ArtaleAI/Core/PathPlanningTracker.cs#471-490)
- [ ] 修正 [SetActiveEdge()](file:///d:/Full_end/C%23/ArtaleAI/Core/PathPlanningTracker.cs#774-855), [UpdatePathState()](file:///d:/Full_end/C%23/ArtaleAI/Core/PathPlanningTracker.cs#1043-1160), [ForceAdvanceTarget()](file:///d:/Full_end/C%23/ArtaleAI/Core/PathPlanningTracker.cs#1302-1317), [Dispose()](file:///d:/Full_end/C%23/ArtaleAI/Core/PathPlanningTracker.cs#1702-1723)

